# Vickers Cottage Inventory & POS System

## Project Overview

Vickers Cottage Inventory & POS System is a web-based inventory management and point-of-sale solution designed for a beverage business that purchases and sells alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks.

The system will help manage:

- Inventory tracking
- Product management
- Supplier management
- Purchase management
- Sales and POS operations
- Profit calculations
- Business reporting
- User and staff management

The application is designed to be accessible from desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

---

## Business Goals

The system aims to:

- Eliminate manual inventory tracking
- Monitor stock levels in real time
- Track purchases from suppliers
- Record customer sales efficiently
- Automatically update inventory after sales
- Generate business reports and insights
- Improve profitability and operational efficiency

